{"tid":2158843,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普：正考慮禁制阿里巴巴 ","createTime":"2020-08-16T03:24:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T15:01:53.000Z","uid":66271,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c27ce961c3b1dbad8b0f59e97bce9fba2a160d38","tid":2158843,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T03:24:49.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普上周五（14日）再簽署行政命令，要求中國字節跳動必須在90日內出售或分拆手機應用程式抖音海外版TikTok的美國業務，最多再延長30天。特朗普昨（15日）在記者會被問到會否考慮禁制其他中資公司如阿里巴巴，他回應說「是的，我們正檢視其他事情」。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普在記者會上又提到中美貿易關係，他嚴厲批評中國，但同時也稱讚中國購買大豆、粟米等農產品。"},{"pid":"da30085091906170c04cc00588f4bb3c38bf937b","tid":2158843,"uid":213913,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T03:29:47.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母啊 侵侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1d25c3f1a137cfd02f6aead8a44c68b7f3f04bb","tid":2158843,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T03:49:28.000Z","msg":"唔制裁正衰仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25072388eed663e698113eb93a7c14f7ee8de7c7","tid":2158843,"uid":42815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T04:00:51.000Z","msg":"又出口遁"},{"pid":"464c7eb6f440f6b7ace3c8619afe9a48ccf6617f","tid":2158843,"uid":310700,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T04:01:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4kD7YJj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4kD7YJj.gif&h=1a8ed1ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c7708bfbc553d4d10e3d54bc39a0897b9f8f72ab","tid":2158843,"uid":211323,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T05:39:54.000Z","msg":"手頭上有幾十手9988<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class